I know, you are confused, because you can't tell the difference between "HIV" and "AIDS".  But can you tell the difference between 400 million and 800 million?  I think so.  That is how much the population of Africa has increased since 1984 !   Fat lot of good that worshiped "AIDS virus" has done.
